					<![CDATA[
						 <p>I absolutely love anything having to do with the antimemetics division, so this really knocked it out of the park for me. Initially I thought this was a rewrite/properly formatted SCP page for 4739 from the Introductory Antimemetics tale, but even as a distinct SCP it's very cool and I enjoyed it a lot. I'd love to see Oz-Ω2 implemented in the existing antimemetics storyline, possibly as a tool to use against 3125 or something. Anyway, long story short, awesome job.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
