				<wikidot:authorName>TL333s</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>1304786</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>It reminds me of a lot of other very meta skips, from 3999 to the one where <em>you are the SCP!!!</em>, but it's entirely different from any of them. So, I guess, in a way, it's that bizarre sense of familiarity with the unfamiliar that leads me to believe that, whatever this is, it's good.</p> 
